#1. Create a greeting for your program.

print("Welcome to THE ULTIMATE Band Name Generator!!!\n")

#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in.

city = input("Okay let's start by telling me the city you grew up in.\n")

#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet.

pet = input("Okay great, now the last thing I need is the name of one of your pets.\n")

#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.

print("Your new band name could be " + city + " " + pet + ".")
